(10, 'menu', 'menu_dis', 35, '\n                        \n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Hair brush is an important tool for maintaining healthy hair. Combing your hair before it dries out can easily break your hair. So if you want to comb your hair when it is wet, you should choose a wide tooth comb (about 2 cm apart from your teeth). After your hair is completely dry, you should choose a hair brush based on your length and shape.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                                            '),
(11, 'menu', 'menu_dis', 36, '\n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The function of the hair comb is far more than combing the hair, it can also be used in your hands as a small health care products, play health, fitness effect.Hair comb can also promote hair growth.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                        '),
(12, 'menu', 'menu_dis', 37, '\n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Personal care scissors can safely trim nose and ear hair and any other personal care area. Use this tool with extreme care and gentleness. Precautions: lightly oil and place in a dry place to prevent rust.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                        '),
(13, 'menu', 'menu_dis', 38, '\n                        \n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Cashmere is one of the few things in your wardrobe that will look better as the years go on. This cashmere comb is all you need to keep your cashmere looking as good as new.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">After wearing your new knitwear garment for the first few times you may find small balls of fibre forming on the surface. This is known as â€˜pillingâ€™ and is caused by the cashmere fibres shedding naturally. This is caused by wearing, not washing and is not a sign of inferior quality. Our cashmere comb can easily remove these and keep your item looking good as new.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                                            '),
(14, 'menu', 'menu_dis', 39, '\n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Foot file through the raised hole to remove old skin, calluses, remove old skin. Calluses are local flat cuticle hyperplasia of hands and feet skin caused by pressure and friction for a long time, which is the protective response of the body. If you don\'t timely clean up and add nutrients to the skin, it will not only affect the beauty of the skin, but also affect the normal walking if it is serious, which can be resolved after the cause.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                        '),
(15, 'menu', 'menu_dis', 41, '\n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The brush head of the nail brush is covered with bristles. Nail brushes are used for nail cleaning. Because fingernail brush has brush hair at the same time and hold the skin bag that has rinse water, use is convenient; The brush head position is set with bulges for removing nail dirt.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                        '),
(16, 'menu', 'menu_dis', 42, '\n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Guasha board is the main instrument for gua sha, the selection of natural quality xuan huang bian stone and natural buffalo horn as raw materials, through the stimulation of the human body related meridian, acupuncture points, so as to achieve the effect of health.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Guasha board has the effect of promoting blood circulation and removing blood stasis, dredging channels and collaterals, promoting qi and relieving pain, clearing heat and detoxifying, strengthening spleen and stomach, harmonizing Yin and Yang, warming channels and dispersing cold, promoting qi and activating blood, enhancing skin permeability, improving viscera function and enhancing immune function.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                        '),
(17, 'menu', 'menu_dis', 43, '\n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The shape of the brush head is usually square and diamond. Square brush heads are effective at cleaning every surface of the teeth. The end of the diamond-shaped brush head is more pointed than the square design, which makes it easier to clean deeply inside the mouth. A tooth brush with a head of any shape can clean teeth, but the size of the head requires a comprehensive consideration of the size of the mouth, the degree of opening and personal habits. Try to use small brush head, so as to be able to go deep into the mouth, ensure flexible rotation, clean back teeth.</span></p><div><br></div><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                    '),
(18, 'menu', 'menu_dis', 48, '\n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Beard brush is a vital tool in helping you tame that rogue hair on your face. Beard brush helps to give your beard a sense of direction, helps to scrape off dead cells that lie lurking in the form of flakes in your beard and also will dislodge any residue of yesterdayâ€™s dinner that you may be harboring in your beard.</span><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                    '),
