(319, 'page_content', 'pcontents', 25, '\n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><div class=\"ablendo wow\" style=\"visibility: visible;animation-name: fadeInUp;animation-duration:3s; animation-delay: 0.2s;\">\n	<div class=\"ablendo-top\">\n	<h2>COMPANY INTRODUCTION</h2>\n	<p>ABLENDO IS A COMPANY FOCUS ON WOMEN\'S COATS &amp; JACKETS.</p>\n	<span>MANUFACTURER</span>\n	<p>ABLENDO is a Coats &amp; Jackets manufacturer, which located in Ningbo, Zhejiang, China ABL ENDO offer different levels of finishes to suit the needs of all our customers.</p>\n	<span>PROFESSION</span>\n	<p>With 15 years of experience in this sector. ABLENDO have excellent teams who care on product development &amp; design, quality control &amp; inspection.</p>\n	<span>DESIGN &amp; SAMPLING</span>\n	<p>ABLENDO is constantly striving to find the latest and best styles for our customers. We not only make samples. But contribute constructive idea on styles and garment solution for your reference.</p></div>\n	\n	\n	<div class=\"abledp-in\">\n	<div class=\"firm-culture\">\n	<div class=\"firm-cont\">\n		<div class=\"firm-top\">\n			<div class=\"firm-top-h2\">\n				\n				<hr>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"firm-top-img\">\n				<img src=\"images/firm-img.png\" alt=\"\">\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"firm-bottom\">\n			<p>If you are looking for a partner with whom to stream line your purchasing processes and achieve greater performance in your business opera-tions. ABL ENDO offers you its know how in order to establish a stable and lasting relationship that is satisfactory and prosperous for your busi-ness.</p>\n			<hr>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n	\n	\n	</div>\n	\n	\n	<div class=\"abledp-bottom wow\" style=\"visibility: visible;animation-name: fadeInUp;animation-duration:3s; animation-delay: 0.2s;\">\n	<h2>HOW WE WORK</h2>\n		<div class=\"abledp-bottom-nr\">\n		<div class=\"abledp-bottom-left\">\n			\n			<img src=\"images/adle.png\" alt=\"tu\">\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"abledp-bottom-right\">\n			<h2>FITTING</h2>\n			<p>With years experience, ABLENDO well know good fting means it will be totally different effect on body with same design. ABL ENDO care about milli-meter difference. Before sending you the sample. We do many times adjust on modal or 3D modal. In order to get good effect.</p>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"abledp-bottom-nr\">\n			<div class=\"abledp-bottom-right\">\n			<h2>FABRIC</h2>\n			<p>Fabric is a main aspect for new fashion style. We care about all the physical and chemical requirement, and do a good control before production.</p>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"abledp-bottom-left\">\n			\n			<img src=\"images/adle1.png\" alt=\"tu\">\n			</div>\n			\n		<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"abledp-boo\">\n			<div class=\"abledp-boo-nr\">\n			<div class=\"abledep-boo-top\">\n				<img src=\"images/abode-boo.png\" alt=\"\">\n				</div>\n				<div class=\"abledep-boo-bottom\">\n					<span>COLOR</span>\n					<p>We are care about color, each time we checked color under our light box. As required D65.</p>\n				</div>\n			\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"abledp-boo-nr ablde-zj\">\n			<div class=\"abledep-boo-top\">\n				<img src=\"images/abode-boo1.png\" alt=\"\">\n				</div>\n				<div class=\"abledep-boo-bottom\">\n					<span>WORKMANSHIP</span>\n					<p>ABLENDO workers care about each part details making.</p>\n				</div>\n			\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"abledp-boo-nr\">\n			<div class=\"abledep-boo-top\">\n				<img src=\"images/abode-boo2.png\" alt=\"\">\n				</div>\n				<div class=\"abledep-boo-bottom\">\n					<span>ENDING</span>\n					<p>We are more than happy to deliver a top garment.</p>\n				</div>\n			\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n		\n		\n		</div>\n<div class=\"faq wow\" style=\"visibility: visible;animation-name: fadeInUp;animation-duration:3s; animation-delay: 0.2s;\">\n	<h2>F&amp;Q</h2>\n		<div class=\"faq-nr\">\n			<div class=\"faq-left\">\n			<img src=\"images/faq.png\" alt=\"\">\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"faq-right\">\n				<div class=\"faq-wb\">\n					<span>SALES PROCEDURESALES PROCEDURE</span>\n					<p>Q: Is there a Minimum Order Quantity?</p>\n					<p>Q: What payment terms are acceptable?</p>\n				\n				</div>\n				<div class=\"faq-wb\">\n					<span>LEAD-TIME AND DELIVERY</span>\n					<p>Q: What are the average lead-times?</p>\n					<p>Q: Is it possible to order goods CIF?</p>\n				\n				</div>\n				<div class=\"faq-wb\">\n					<span>PRIVATE LABEL AND ARTWORK DESIGNS</span>\n					<p>Q: Can Ningbo TOP help me prepare graphic designs?</p>\n					<p>Q: What should I be aware of when providing Artwork Design and Technical Files?</p>\n				\n				</div>\n			\n			\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n\n\n	\n	\n	</div>\n		<div class=\"faq-bottom\">\n	<div class=\"faq-bottom-wb\">\n			<span>BUILDING YoU A COLLECTION</span>\n		<div class=\"faq-bottom-img\">\n		\n		<img src=\"images/faq1.png\">\n		</div>\n		<p>You want to make your own label? We can make you a collection that will fit your costumers and their needs.</p>\n			\n			\n			</div>\n			\n				<div class=\"faq-bottom-wb fqa-ts\">\n			<span>SELLING OUR 0WN COLLECTION</span>\n		<div class=\"faq-bottom-img\">\n		\n		<img src=\"images/faq2.png\">\n		</div>\n		<p>We create our own collection for men,women &amp; chil-dren, inspired by the latest trends from Europe, the US and Asia. If you like something from our collectu-on you can pick it out and add it to your new collec-tion</p>\n			\n			\n			</div>\n			\n				<div class=\"faq-bottom-wb\">\n			<span>ALTERING DESIGNS</span>\n		<div class=\"faq-bottom-img\">\n		\n		<img src=\"images/faq3.png\">\n		</div>\n		<p>You like a design but you don\'thave a designer?ourdesigner will work with you to create the design youimagine</p>\n			\n			\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n	\n	</div>\n\n		</div>\n\n\n	\n	</div>\n	\n	</div>\n\n<p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                                                                                    '),
